<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
                <i class="fas fa-bug"></i> Bug Bounty Lab
            </a>
            <div class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                <a class="nav-link" href="/">Dashboard</a>
                <% if (user) { %>
                    <span class="navbar-text me-3">Welcome, <%= user.username %>!</span>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/auth/logout">Logout</a>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/auth/login">Login</a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mt-4">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="jumbotron bg-danger text-white p-5 rounded mb-4">
                    <h1 class="display-4">
                        <i class="fas fa-database"></i> SQL Injection Lab
                    </h1>
                    <p class="lead">Practice various SQL injection techniques in a controlled environment.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="alert alert-warning">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> Learning Objectives</h4>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li>Understand how SQL injection vulnerabilities occur</li>
                        <li>Learn different types of SQL injection attacks</li>
                        <li>Practice payload construction and testing</li>
                        <li>Understand the impact of SQL injection vulnerabilities</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6 col-xl-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
                        <h5 class="card-title mb-0">
                            <i class="fas fa-search"></i> Basic Search
                        </h5>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="card-text">Practice basic SQL injection on a product search functionality.</p>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <strong>Techniques:</strong>
                            <div class="mt-1">
                                <span class="badge bg-light text-dark me-1 mb-1">String Concatenation</span>
                                <span class="badge bg-light text-dark me-1 mb-1">Comment Injection</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer bg-transparent">
                        <a href="/sql-injection/search" class="btn btn-outline-primary w-100">
                            <i class="fas fa-play"></i> Start Challenge
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-6 col-xl-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-header bg-success text-white">
                        <h5 class="card-title mb-0">
                            <i class="fas fa-link"></i> Union-based
                        </h5>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="card-text">Learn union-based SQL injection to extract data from multiple tables.</p>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <strong>Techniques:</strong>
                            <div class="mt-1">
                                <span class="badge bg-light text-dark me-1 mb-1">UNION SELECT</span>
                                <span class="badge bg-light text-dark me-1 mb-1">Column Counting</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer bg-transparent">
                        <a href="/sql-injection/union" class="btn btn-outline-success w-100">
                            <i class="fas fa-play"></i> Start Challenge
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-6 col-xl-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-header bg-warning text-dark">
                        <h5 class="card-title mb-0">
                            <i class="fas fa-eye-slash"></i> Boolean-based Blind
                        </h5>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="card-text">Practice boolean-based blind SQL injection techniques.</p>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <strong>Techniques:</strong>
                            <div class="mt-1">
                                <span class="badge bg-light text-dark me-1 mb-1">AND/OR Logic</span>
                                <span class="badge bg-light text-dark me-1 mb-1">Substring Extraction</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer bg-transparent">
                        <a href="/sql-injection/boolean" class="btn btn-outline-warning w-100">
                            <i class="fas fa-play"></i> Start Challenge
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-6 col-xl-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-header bg-info text-white">
                        <h5 class="card-title mb-0">
                            <i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Time-based Blind
                        </h5>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="card-text">Learn time-based blind SQL injection using delays.</p>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <strong>Techniques:</strong>
                            <div class="mt-1">
                                <span class="badge bg-light text-dark me-1 mb-1">SLEEP()</span>
                                <span class="badge bg-light text-dark me-1 mb-1">Time Delays</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer bg-transparent">
                        <a href="/sql-injection/time" class="btn btn-outline-info w-100">
                            <i class="fas fa-play"></i> Start Challenge
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-6 col-xl-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-header bg-danger text-white">
                        <h5 class="card-title mb-0">
                            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i> Error-based
                        </h5>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="card-text">Practice error-based SQL injection to extract information.</p>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <strong>Techniques:</strong>
                            <div class="mt-1">
                                <span class="badge bg-light text-dark me-1 mb-1">Error Messages</span>
                                <span class="badge bg-light text-dark me-1 mb-1">Information Extraction</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer bg-transparent">
                        <a href="/sql-injection/error" class="btn btn-outline-danger w-100">
                            <i class="fas fa-play"></i> Start Challenge
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-6 col-xl-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-header bg-dark text-white">
                        <h5 class="card-title mb-0">
                            <i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> Advanced
                        </h5>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="card-text">Advanced SQL injection techniques with multiple tables.</p>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <strong>Techniques:</strong>
                            <div class="mt-1">
                                <span class="badge bg-light text-dark me-1 mb-1">Multi-table</span>
                                <span class="badge bg-light text-dark me-1 mb-1">Complex Queries</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer bg-transparent">
                        <a href="/sql-injection/advanced" class="btn btn-outline-dark w-100">
                            <i class="fas fa-play"></i> Start Challenge
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mt-4">
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="alert alert-info">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> Tips for Success</h4>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li>Start with basic injection and work your way up to advanced techniques</li>
                        <li>Use browser developer tools to inspect the SQL queries being executed</li>
                        <li>Try different payloads and observe the responses</li>
                        <li>Document your findings as you would in a real penetration test</li>
                        <li>Remember: This is a learning environment - experiment freely!</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="bg-dark text-white text-center py-3 mt-5">
        <div class="container">
            <p class="mb-0">&copy; 2024 Bug Bounty Lab. Educational purposes only.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
